 {changeFlag}‚ÜêMassageConfig filename;config
‚çù Checks whether the config data comes with all expected entries.
‚çù If anything is missing (late arrivals) those are added.
‚çù Returns a 1 in case data was added, otherwise 0.
 changeFlag‚Üê0
 config‚ÜêGet_JSON5 filename
 :If 0=config.CIDER.‚éïNC'tests'
     config.CIDER.tests‚Üê''
